                <h3>Information regarding Backups</h3>
                <p>Due to storage concerns, your backup will be automatically deleted 2 hours after you generate the file. After you click "Backup Server"
                    please wait 10 minutes for the file to be fully generated before you download the file. You can access your backup with FileZilla at this path: /ftp/backup </p>
